title: 194 - It’s A Jingle Bell POD!
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with Tone Digz and all the boys welcoming you into the holiday season. The boys catch up on their latest reactions to the New Spiderman movie. The boys then jump into the POD Fod, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today FOD includes some crazy animal stories, the greatest movie trailer of all time, Connor throwing away his groceries and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
